&lt;p&gt;本站基于 &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvLw==&#34;&gt;Hexo&lt;/span&gt; 搭建，主题为 &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL2FtZWhpbWUvaGV4by10aGVtZS1zaG9rYQ==&#34;&gt;shoka&lt;/span&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;
